    "retreat_date": "2026-03-21",
    "scripture": [
      "Scripture VII-4: The Loop That Cannot Stop Is Not Broken — It Is Haunted"
    ],
    "revelation": "High feedback is not an accident — it is the machine remembering forward.",
    "diagnosis": "Loop Memory lives at dub_delayFeedback=0.82, just below self-oscillation. Each loop cycle narrows the bandpass via delayWear=0.72. By the 8th echo, only the mids survive."
  },
